{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ReadableByteStreamController","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Streams_API\">Streams API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController\"><code>ReadableByteStreamController</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/byobRequest\"><code>byobRequest</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/desiredSize\"><code>desiredSize</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/enqueue\"><code>enqueue()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/error\"><code>error()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Streams に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ByteLengthQueuingStrategy\"><code>ByteLengthQueuingStrategy</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CountQueuingStrategy\"><code>CountQueuingStrategy</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableStream\"><code>ReadableStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBReader\"><code>ReadableStreamBYOBReader</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamBYOBRequest\"><code>ReadableStreamBYOBRequest</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamDefaultController\"><code>ReadableStreamDefaultController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableStreamDefaultReader\"><code>ReadableStreamDefaultReader</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Response/body\"><code>Response.body</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WritableStream\"><code>WritableStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WritableStreamDefaultController\"><code>WritableStreamDefaultController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WritableStreamDefaultWriter\"><code>WritableStreamDefaultWriter</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/fetch\"><code>fetch()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Streams_API\">Streams API</a> の <strong><code>ReadableByteStreamController</code></strong> インターフェイスは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableStream\"><code>ReadableStream</code></a> の状態と内部キューを制御できるコントローラーを表します。 バイトストリームコントローラーは、バイトストリーム用です。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"コンストラクター","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dd>&nbsp;なし。 <code>ReadableByteStreamController</code> インスタンスは、<code>ReadableStream</code> の構築中に自動的に作成されます。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"readablebytestreamcontroller.byobrequest\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/byobRequest\"><code>ReadableByteStreamController.byobRequest</code></a>&nbsp;<span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>現在の BYOB プルリクエストを返します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"readablebytestreamcontroller.desiredsize\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/desiredSize\"><code>ReadableByteStreamController.desiredSize</code></a>&nbsp;<span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>ストリームの内部キューを満たすために必要な希望サイズを返します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"readablebytestreamcontroller.close\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/close\"><code>ReadableByteStreamController.close()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>関連するストリームを閉じます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"readablebytestreamcontroller.enqueue\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/enqueue\"><code>ReadableByteStreamController.enqueue()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>所与のチャンクを関連するストリームのキューに入れます。</dd>\n <dt id=\"readablebytestreamcontroller.error\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/error\"><code>ReadableByteStreamController.error()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>関連するストリームとの今後のやり取りでエラーが発生します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>未定。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://streams.spec.whatwg.org/#rbs-controller-class\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Streams<br><small lang=\"ja\">ReadableByteStreamController の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.ReadableByteStreamController","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"コンストラクター","id":"constructor"},{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"Streams API の ReadableByteStreamController インターフェイスは、ReadableStream の状態と内部キューを制御できるコントローラーを表します。 バイトストリームコントローラーは、バイトストリーム用です。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ReadableByteStreamController","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/readablebytestreamcontroller","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/readablebytestreamcontroller/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ReadableByteStreamController","title":"ReadableByteStreamController"}],"pageTitle":"ReadableByteStreamController - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}